{"title":"Cameron Hayman","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Cameron Hayman","format":"html"},"headingText":"Areas of Focus","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n<div style=\"\n  max-width: 660px;\n  margin: 0 auto 28px auto;\n  background: #396896;\n  color: #fff;\n  font-size: 1.40rem;\n  font-style: italic;\n  font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n  letter-spacing: 0.4px;\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.13);\n  padding: 16px 32px 14px 32px;\n  text-align: center;\">\n  \"Building systematic trading systems at the intersection of research and execution.\"\n</div>\n\n\n---\n\n\n::: {.columns}\n::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n- **Statistical Arbitrage**  \n  Multi-leg, mean-reverting, market-neutral strategies\n- **Machine Learning & Alpha**  \n  Predictive modeling, feature engineering, risk analytics\n:::\n::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n- **Real-Time Execution Systems**  \n  Automated infra, backtesting, live dashboards\n- **Alternative Data & NLP**  \n  Sentiment, event-driven pipelines, unstructured data\n:::\n:::\n\n---\n\n<div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n  <img src=\"images/LII-MSI.png\" alt=\"Statistical Arbitrage Multi-Panel Plot\" style=\"max-width: 900px; width: 100%; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 6px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);\" />\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; color: #b0b0b0;\">\n  <em>**LII-MSI Pairing:** Multi-leg, laddered, stat-arb strat: *PnL: 1375.99, Sharpe: 3.29; Rolling: 3.09, Total Trades: 104.*</em>\n</div>\n\n---\n\n## About\n\nQuantitative Researcher specializing in **designing, validating, and deploying production-grade trading strategies**.  \nPassionate about bridging the gap between rigorous research and real-world trading performance.\n\n---\n\n## Connect\n\nExplore my featured projects, detailed backtests, and open-source code.  \nFeel free to connect!\n\n[![GitHub](https://img.shields.io/badge/GitHub-Portfolio-181717?logo=github&logoColor=white)](https://github.com/chayman7771)\n[![LinkedIn](https://img.shields.io/badge/LinkedIn-Connect-0A66C2?logo=linkedin&logoColor=white)](https://www.linkedin.com/in/cameron-hayman-27a7a6155?lipi=urn%3Ali%3Apage%3Ad_flagship3_profile_view_base_contact_details%3BtSWkT3hfT9StBMVtbLiTnA%3D%3D)\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n<div style=\"\n  max-width: 660px;\n  margin: 0 auto 28px auto;\n  background: #396896;\n  color: #fff;\n  font-size: 1.40rem;\n  font-style: italic;\n  font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n  letter-spacing: 0.4px;\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.13);\n  padding: 16px 32px 14px 32px;\n  text-align: center;\">\n  \"Building systematic trading systems at the intersection of research and execution.\"\n</div>\n\n\n---\n\n## Areas of Focus\n\n::: {.columns}\n::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n- **Statistical Arbitrage**  \n  Multi-leg, mean-reverting, market-neutral strategies\n- **Machine Learning & Alpha**  \n  Predictive modeling, feature engineering, risk analytics\n:::\n::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n- **Real-Time Execution Systems**  \n  Automated infra, backtesting, live dashboards\n- **Alternative Data & NLP**  \n  Sentiment, event-driven pipelines, unstructured data\n:::\n:::\n\n---\n\n<div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n  <img src=\"images/LII-MSI.png\" alt=\"Statistical Arbitrage Multi-Panel Plot\" style=\"max-width: 900px; width: 100%; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 6px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);\" />\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; color: #b0b0b0;\">\n  <em>**LII-MSI Pairing:** Multi-leg, laddered, stat-arb strat: *PnL: 1375.99, Sharpe: 3.29; Rolling: 3.09, Total Trades: 104.*</em>\n</div>\n\n---\n\n## About\n\nQuantitative Researcher specializing in **designing, validating, and deploying production-grade trading strategies**.  \nPassionate about bridging the gap between rigorous research and real-world trading performance.\